title: The Romantic Age (1927 film)
text: The Romantic Age is a 1927 American <a href="silent%20film">silent</a> <a href="drama%20film">drama film</a> directed by <a href="Robert%20Florey">Robert Florey</a> and starring <a href="Eugene%20O%27Brien%20%28actor%29">Eugene O'Brien</a>, <a href="Alberta%20Vaughn">Alberta Vaughn</a> and <a href="Bert%20Woodruff">Bert Woodruff</a>.
